author: jeremy_a
msg: GuiTest.jmx has all JMeter GUI components in a single test plan.  (Actually it doesn't yet have the protocol-specific components.  I'll add those later.)
You aren't intended to actually run this test plan -- instead, you can use it to quickly check the effects of layout changes on each component.
The components are structured in a tree similar to the JMeter package structure, and each component has a name similar to the component's class name.
